msg: Fix issue #1994:  'svn cp wc URL' bug;  fix incorrect out-of-dateness check.
out-of-dateness check not only when the parent dir is copied, but
when *any* parent dir is copied.  In other words, directory batons
should be inheriting the 'was_copied' flags from parents.
